title: AwesomeBlog
subtitle: blogging platform
---

Blogging platform based on Django 1.8

## Features
 * Create and manage blog (one or more)
 * Create and manage post
 * Author profile
 * Manage autor profile
 * Manage comments above posts
 * Login / Registration


